'''氯酸亚锡'''是一种无机化合物，化学式为Sn(ClO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>，其中锡的[[化合价|化合价]]为+2价，不稳定。

有文献对其ΔH<sub>f</sub><sup>θ</sup>进行计算，−ΔH<sub>f</sub><sup>θ</sup>(Sn(ClO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>) = 46±15 Kcal/mol。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Industrial & Engineering Chemistry|volume=55|issue=7|language=en|issn=0019-7866|date=1963-7|pages=32–39|doi=10.1021/ie50643a006|url=http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ie50643a006|title=COMPUTER ESTIMATION OF HEAT AND FREE ENERGY OF FORMATION FOR SIMPLE INORGANIC COMPOUNDS|accessdate=2019-02-25|author=D. E. Wilcox, L. A. Bromley|archive-date=2019-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130203638/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ie50643a006|dead-url=no}}</ref>一份专利指出，氯酸亚锡可以作为加速紫外线固化作用的催化剂组分之一。<ref>Yu, Zongping; Yang, Jun. Catalyst for accelerating UV-​crosslinking and preparation method thereof. 2010. CN 101786021</ref>
